  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Daylight brings opportunity and nightfall, danger.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/92585f97ac744eb1518ed61e3f74284c.webp?t=1734372830\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/92585f97ac744eb1518ed61e3f74284c.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" class=\"bb_img\" width=609 height=174 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources and strategically build up your viking settlement by day, fortifying it to withstand the relentless onslaught of skeletons by night. But your task doesn't end there, build tent for your followers assign them to do vital task such as logging, mining, archery and being warriors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/b159ec764fa57551df435cd92c986b7e.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/b159ec764fa57551df435cd92c986b7e.webm?t=1734372830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base building</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower defense</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource gathering</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural generation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/7248542b88b311b4716dae56c88b0903.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/7248542b88b311b4716dae56c88b0903.webm?t=1734372830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/7248542b88b311b4716dae56c88b0903.mp4?t=1734372830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Daylight brings opportunity and nightfall, danger.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/92585f97ac744eb1518ed61e3f74284c.webp?t=1734372830\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/92585f97ac744eb1518ed61e3f74284c.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" class=\"bb_img\" width=609 height=174 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources and strategically build up your viking settlement by day, fortifying it to withstand the relentless onslaught of skeletons by night. But your task doesn't end there, build tent for your followers assign them to do vital task such as logging, mining, archery and being warriors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/b159ec764fa57551df435cd92c986b7e.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/b159ec764fa57551df435cd92c986b7e.webm?t=1734372830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base building</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower defense</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource gathering</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural generation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013190/extras/7248542b88b311b4716dae56c88b0903.poster.avif?t=1734372830\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste